<ptxt>
<emph etype = "bold">
B1951: Ignition Power Supply Voltage Data Malfunction
</emph>
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Headlight auto leveling and washer control module power supply circuit voltage is higher than 16.4 V for 10 sec.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Headlight auto leveling and washer control module power supply circuit voltage is lower than 9.3 V for 10 sec.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
